msg: Whenever files are uploaded or dropped into the deploy folder, make sure they do not overwrite an existing file when they are moved into the uploaded folder. This includes updated files, so previous versions of widget packages will remain in the uploaded location but the metadata will point to the updated version. See WOOKIE-402.
